{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"mode":2,"scripts":[{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"祭儀主催担当の駿河です。長旅お疲れ様でございます。三笠様、そして翔鶴さんに瑞鶴さん","dir":1,"bgm":"cw-battle-boss","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":305140},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"お主は噂の紀伊型三番艦駿河か。うむ、百聞は一見に如かず――祭儀の準備、誠に大儀である。重桜の仲間に代わって感謝するぞ","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ありがとうございます。自分は並み居る重桜の艦船の一人としてやるべきことをしたまでで、別に褒められるようなことは…","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":305140,"side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"ははは。謙遜も過ぎると卑屈になるぞ。聞いた話によれば合同演習の準備事務だけでなく、自ら参加も申し出たそうではないか","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"は、はぁい……そういうことになっていますね","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":305140,"side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"say":"演習とはいえ、他陣営の参加者もいる以上重桜の威光を示さねばならぬ。お主の力を試す故、我らと一回手合わせするのはどうかな？","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"（え！いきなり！？こういうタイプはちょっと苦手だけど…！）","dir":1,"side":1,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":20}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":305140},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"あ！今「え！いきなり！？」って心の中で叫んだな！","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"（なんでわかったの！？）","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":3,"x":20}],"actor":305140},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"「なんでわかった！？」って心で言ってそうだな。心が読みやす過ぎるのは感心しないな、まったく、最近の若者は…","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"say":"…っ！こんな質問をして恐縮ですが、どうして…わかったのですか？","actor":305140,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"場数ってやつかな。戦場で敵の心を読もうと努力し続ければいずれ、コツがつかめるようになる","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"座学での成績が抜群だと聞いておる。どれ、この我が実戦というものを教えてやろう！","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":1,"x":0}],"say":"三笠様が直々にご教示くださるのでしたら、こっちも全力を出させていただきます…！","actor":305140,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"その心意気だ。さあ、かかってくるがよい！","actor":305110,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"（三笠様相手に手を抜いてしまうとバレるに決まっている。本当の本当に、全力を出す…！）","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":305140,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"戦艦駿河、参ります…！","actor":305140,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"}],"fadein":1.5,"id":"FUYINGYINGHUA6"}